title: Ep 33: The Sea Shanty
description:
Today's proceedings:  Josh creates a masterpiece, a man learns he shouldn't ask about previous partners, a mother goes above and beyond for her daughter, and we discover a new subreddit called the 10th dentist.  We also have some fun discussing some unfun facts.   Rate and Review our podcast and share it with your friends!
